{
  "to": ["mark@beaconofhope.org"],
  "subject": "Client Progress Updates – Thomas & Emily",
  "body": "Hi Mark,

Hope you’re doing well. I wanted to share a brief progress update on Thomas and Emily ahead of our next check-in.

Thomas:
• He continues to attend sessions regularly and is showing increasing engagement in group discussions, even taking on informal peer-support roles.
• We’re focusing on building coping strategies to manage occasional self-doubt and anxiety; overall trajectory remains positive.

Emily:
• Attendance remains consistent and she reports feeling encouraged.
• She’s expressed interest in community volunteering to broaden her support network; we’re exploring suitable opportunities.

Next steps:
• I’ll monitor how Thomas responds to the new grounding exercises we introduced and will keep you posted.
• For Emily, I’ll send you potential volunteer program options once we confirm her preferences.

Let me know if Beacon of Hope has any additional insights or resources that could support either client. Happy to discuss further on our next call.

Best,
Jane
",
